data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
There is a scam circulating on the internet, where a "virus" automatically detects a BITCOIN wallet in your WINDOWS transfer area, and CHANGES the copied BITCOIN address to a hacker's BITCOIN address in which you can confuse yourself and to make a wrong transfer :(
Do the test yourself:
1 - Open the program. 2- Copy a BTC address with CTRL + C. 3- And paste the address anywhere.
Okay, you'll see that the address has changed :(
